channel.title: Massing multiplying?
channel.description: Ok, this is not good. I was minding my own bussiness, when i noticed shops in the wrong place, and nulls everywhere. Then, i noticed that there were 14 people online, then all of a sudden 40 people!! I was like what in the hell. I looked on the list, and half of them were nulls. The next second, there were 60 players online. It lagged my computer and my server so bad i shut it down. Whats the problem?
